Citation.sTitle: Enthalpy of mixing of liquid Ni-Ti-Zr alloys at 1873 K
Citation.sAbstract: The enthalpies of mixing of liquid Ni Ti Zr alloys were determined at 1873 K by means of a hightemperature isoperibolic calorimeter. The investigations were performed along sections xNi/xTi = 4/1 and xNi/xZr = 4/1 in the corresponding composition ranges xZr = 0 0.41 and xTi = 0 0.48. The limiting partial enthalpy of mixing of undercooled liquid zirconium in liquid Ni Ti alloy is ( 192 +- 8) kJ mol 1. The limiting partial enthalpy of mixing of undercooled liquid titanium in liquid Ni Zr alloy is ( 130 +- 12) kJ mol 1. The integral mixing enthalpies are negative over the investigated composition range. An analytical expression for the representation of the integral mixing enthalpy was obtained and used for the calculation of the function in the whole composition range.
